Global Polyester Yarns Market Insights
Polyester Yarns Market size was valued at USD 60 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 80 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Polyester Yarns Market Overview
The global polyester yarns market size was valued at USD 58.76 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2023 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for polyester yarns in the textile, automotive, and home furnishings industries. Polyester yarns are widely recognized for their durability, strength, and cost-effectiveness. Key applications in apparel and industrial sectors are projected to remain strong, further propelling market expansion. The growing emphasis on eco-friendly and sustainable products also plays a significant role in shaping market dynamics. With significant advancements in manufacturing technologies, polyester yarns are expected to experience strong growth across various regions, especially in emerging markets.

